Author: pusspusskushkush
Text: Things like that are shitty to say, but I think (at least for me and my parents) it comes from a place of love. Like they want to acknowledge it, but it can be a difficult topic.

Author: bedbitch
Text: I'm sorry that your mom reacted that way. That's really insensitive. Good for you for eating regular meals and for taking steps toward recovery!
